    <title>latex编辑器配置</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</id>
    <published>2025-09-28T05:26:58.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-09-28T07:43:10.745Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="latex编辑器配置"><a href="#latex编辑器配置" class="headerlink" title="latex编辑器配置"></a>latex编辑器配置</h1><h2 id="Texlive-2025安装"><a href="#Texlive-2025安装" class="headerlink" title="Texlive 2025安装"></a>Texlive 2025安装</h2><h3 id="基础安装"><a href="#基础安装" class="headerlink" title="基础安装"></a>基础安装</h3><p>如果有加速器工具可以从官网下载，如果没有，使用清华大学的开源软件镜像进行下载</p><p><a href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/CTAN/systems/texlive/Images/">Index of &#x2F;CTAN&#x2F;systems&#x2F;texlive&#x2F;Images&#x2F; | 清华大学开源软件镜像站 | Tsinghua Open Source Mirror</a></p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/1.png" alt="image-20250928134534242"></p><p>找到下载的程序的位置，右键点击装载</p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/2.png" alt="image-20250928135937733"></p><p>之后双击 <strong>install-tl-windows.bat</strong> 文件</p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/3.png" alt="image-20250928140258495"></p><p>之后就会出现安装界面，在这个界面我们需要设定两个位置</p><blockquote><ol><li>将软件安装的位置换到<strong>C盘</strong>以外</li><li>在custom设定中只保留中文和英文两种语言【非必要，为了节省内存】</li></ol></blockquote><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928141030681.png" alt="image-20250928141030681"></p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928141120545.png" alt="image-20250928141120545"></p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928141150595.png" alt="image-20250928141150595"></p><p>在设定完这几步之后点击安装 之后便是漫长的等待……..</p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928141318263.png" alt="image-20250928141318263"></p><p>等待安装完毕之后点击关闭即可</p><h3 id="环境变量配置"><a href="#环境变量配置" class="headerlink" title="环境变量配置"></a>环境变量配置</h3><p>演示用机为Win10</p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928151907266.png" alt="image-20250928151907266"></p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928152003973.png" alt="image-20250928152003973"></p><p>找到系统变量中的Path，之后点击编辑</p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928152117429.png" alt="image-20250928152117429"></p><p>之后点击新建，将路径（<strong>F:\Latex\texlive\2025</strong>\bin\windows–将加粗部分改为自己在安装开始时选定的位置），之后粘贴进去尽可，之后点击确定即可</p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928152149098.png" alt="image-20250928152149098"></p><p>鼠标同时按下win + R 输入cmd</p><p> <img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928152445114.png" alt="image-20250928152445114"></p><p>之后输入</p><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">latex -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928152615366.png" alt="image-20250928152615366"></p><h2 id="TexStudio安装"><a href="#TexStudio安装" class="headerlink" title="TexStudio安装"></a>TexStudio安装</h2><p><a href="https://texstudio.sourceforge.net/">TeXstudio - A LaTeX editor</a><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928153041932.png" alt="image-20250928153041932"></p><p>选择适合自己设备的版本进行安装</p><p>注意：在安装的时候注意改下安装的位置，尽量不要安装在C盘中</p><p>安装完成之后打开</p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928153309283.png" alt="image-20250928153309283"></p><p>接下来，快速开启你的写作之路吧！后续会更新如何使用TexStudio，敬请期待吧！</p><p>注意事项：</p><ul><li>全英文路径，尽量不要出现中文路径</li></ul><h2 id="测试"><a href="#测试" class="headerlink" title="测试"></a>测试</h2><blockquote><p>可能大家会担心是否真的安装成功了，我们下面做一个简单的测试！</p></blockquote><p>我们打开【TeXworks editor】程序</p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928153925691.png" alt="image-20250928153925691"></p><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928154039835.png" alt="image-20250928154039835"></p><p>输入代码框中的测试代码：</p><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\documentclass[UTF8]&#123;ctexart&#125;</span><br><span class="line">\<span class="built_in">title</span>&#123;hello，world<span class="variable">!&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">\author&#123;Hilbob&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">\date&#123;\today&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">\begin&#123;document&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">\maketitle</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">你好，世界!</span></span><br><span class="line">\end&#123;document&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/2025/09/28/latex%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20250928154206410.png" alt="image-20250928154206410"></p><p>出现上述界面，就表示成功了！</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">本篇文章详细地演示了如何正确地安装latex环境</summary>
    
    
    
